track.name: I don't wanna do this anymore

wiki.summary: Geneva, X’s ex-girlfriend, is the one who reported that this song wasn’t about anybody in particular. Jahseh just decided to sing a horror love song as soon as he heard the beat, but only Jahseh knows what picture he is painting here. The cover art is a picture of X he probably took himself. Two of his tattoos can be seen: “Cleopatra,” the name of his mother on his chest, and “Wing Ridden Angel” on his right arm, referring to the girlfriend he had before Geneva. Read more on Last.fm.
